## upstream patches
# https://github.com/dajobe/raptor/commit/590681e546cd9aa18d57dc2ea1858cb734a3863f
Patch1: 0001-Calcualte-max-nspace-declarations-correctly-for-XML-.patch
# https://bugs.librdf.org/mantis/view.php?id=650
